## Practical 9 â€“ K-Means Clustering

This practical implements the K-means clustering algorithm from first principles and evaluates clustering performance using cluster purity.

### Key tasks
- Implement K-means clustering with iterative centroid updates
- Assign clusters using Euclidean distance
- Evaluate clustering quality using purity
- Visualise cluster assignments and centroids

